-- Hungary’s Est Media Declines for Fourth Day to Lowest on Record
-- B y   A n d r a s   G e r g e l y
-- 2012-04-24T07:52:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-24/hungary-s-est-media-declines-for-fourth-day-to-lowest-on-record.html
Est Media Vagyonkezelo Nyrt., a
Hungarian entertainment company, declined for a fourth day to
the lowest on record.  The shares of Est Media, which organizes  Hungary ’s biggest
outdoor music festival, dropped as much as 13 percent and traded
6 percent lower at 78 forint by 9:43 a.m. in Budapest.  No bids were accepted at an auction of the company’s shares
on the Budapest Stock Exchange on April 20.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andras Gergely in Budapest at 
